{
  "stem": "14251.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The people drank machine oil from the locomotive and I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The dead people in the, in the cattle car, we had to throw out, you know, every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was no bathroom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I had a coat that someone had made for me out of a plaid blanket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And someone stole my coat while I fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, you had to keep everything close to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's always the same, this camp, that camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It's always the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The problems are the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then the petrifying thing, my mother goes off to try to find something to eat and-- you know, anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the train gets in motion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I know I'm going to go to Timbuktu, and my mother is going to be left behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'd already had enough of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And somehow, by a miracle, she appeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That's all I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we did get after-- we were incubated in West-- in East Germany for a time because of this typhus.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had to contact our same old rescuers, Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Abegg and Hilda [NON-ENGLISH], later Arnold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they, again, provided the money for a train ticket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And again, we had to leave that place illegally because the quarantine time wasn't up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "However, we had sense enough to know if we stayed, we would soon get the typhus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And so we made a dash for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The interesting thing is we're highly law-abiding people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "This had no impact on our conduct later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In fact, it was hard enough to have to do that during those times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So back to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had never been to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to lie about when we came.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
